longBusinessSummary: Sanghi Industries Limited manufactures and markets cement and clinker in India and internationally. The company offers ordinary Portland, Pozzolana Portland, and Portland slag cement products. It also offers Shakti Rath, a mobile technical assessment lab for on-demand onsite concrete testing, and customer care solutions. The company was incorporated in 1985 and is based in Ahmedabad, India. Sanghi Industries Limited operates as a subsidiary of Ambuja Cements Limited.
